column5: Anyone in the Brantford area willing to supervise? I cant use anyone in my family...Go figure  P.s I have a cpon code that saves 15 bucks its jfm969 just enter the code b4 you pay up
a good neighbour or friend can supervise!
Ya I just paid up and have no one here..oh well I can test any time now that im paid up.
I'm in Paris.. PM me and we'll see what we can set up
I did mine with a supervisor that was 120 miles away
How did you do that? just called them and the super has to be present at the time of the test.
I called in for advice about the supervisor thing as well.I think he was drunk.Yelling at his kids and I heard a game on the tele.  And he told me (shhhhhhhhh as well)

Haven't you got a cat or dog or a goldfish?
Funny here I was taking this seroius. It seems as thou most take this as a joke. Although the test was rather simple I was glad to have taken it the right way.
the whole process is a joke...
There was a test???   I thought you just gave $$ and got the card....
I agree it now is... I got mine right when it came out - had to take the test in a classroom.  Anyone can get one now that you can do it online with a "supervisor".
You are right about that.  Just put a buddies name and address in like the vast majority of people do and you're good to go. Unless you don't have any friends?  Dirk

i registered as a supervisor, and people were bringing me there codes for the test...i would do it in 5 minutes, and then get reimbursed for it....up here, the majority of the test is useless to us...there are no beacons, buoys or for the most part lack of high traffic areas.  our buoys consists of empty javax and tide bottles
